item.title: Trend of google-apps-script Tag on Stackoverflow
item.description: Gists March 25, 2019 Published. Kanshi Tanaike Introduction At Stackoverflow, a lot of people post the questions and answers to the questions every day. There are various tags in Stackoverflow. A lot of discussions are performed at each tag. Their discussions bring the important information and are much useful for a lot of people. As one of tags, there is “google-apps-script”. I sometimes discuss at the questions with that tag.
